{"list":[{"title":"目的","data":"<p><span style=\"font-size:28px\">掌握氯离子的检验方法。</span></p>"},{"title":"原理","data":"<p><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">CaCl<sub>2&nbsp;</sub>+ 2AgNO<sub>3&nbsp;</sub>= Ca(NO<sub>3</sub>)<sub>2&nbsp;</sub>+ 2AgCl&darr;</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">MgCl<sub>2&nbsp;</sub>+ 2AgNO<sub>3&nbsp;</sub>= Mg(NO<sub>3</sub>)<sub>2&nbsp;</sub>+ 2AgCl&darr;</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">NaCl + AgNO<sub>3&nbsp;</sub>= NaNO<sub>3&nbsp;</sub>+ AgCl&darr;</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">Na<sub>2</sub>CO<sub>3&nbsp;</sub>+ 2AgNO<sub>3</sub>&nbsp;= 2NaNO<sub>3</sub>&nbsp;+ Ag<sub>2</sub>CO<sub>3</sub>&darr;</span></span></p>"},{"title":"用品","data":"<p><span style=\"font-size:28px\">仪器：试管。</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:28px\">药品：稀盐酸、氯化钠溶液、碳酸钠溶液、自来水、蒸馏水、硝酸银溶液、稀硝酸。</span></p>"},{"title":"步骤","data":"<p><span style=\"font-size:28px\">在五支试管中分别加入少量稀盐酸、氯化钠溶液、碳酸钠溶液、自来水、蒸馏水，然后各滴入几滴硝酸银溶液，观察实验现象。然后再分别加入少量稀硝酸，观察实验现象。</span></p>"},{"title":"现象","data":"<table align=\"center\" border=\"1\" style=\"width:650px\">\n\t<tbody>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align:center\">&nbsp;</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">加入硝酸银溶液后</span></td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">加入稀硝酸后</span></td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">稀盐酸</span></td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">产生白色沉淀</span></td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">沉淀不溶解</span></td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">氯化钠溶液</span></td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">产生白色沉淀</span></td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">沉淀不溶解</span></td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">碳酸钠溶液</span></td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">产生白色沉淀</span></td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">沉淀溶解，产生气泡</span></td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">自来水</span></td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">产生白色沉淀</span></td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">沉淀不溶解</span></td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">蒸馏水</span></td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">无明显现象</span></td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">无明显现象</span></td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>"}],"x":0,"y":0,"width":600,"height":600}